.TH "forceStepUp" "1" "" "SequoiaDB User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
forceStepUp \- force the standby node to be upgraded to the primary node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]db.forceStepUp([options])\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
Sdb
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This function is used to force a standby node to be upgraded to the primary node
in a replication group that does not meet the election conditions.
Please use this command with caution.
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
.TS
